### 1. Successful Registration (Should return 201 Created)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "lizizizi@gmail.com",
  "password": "222",
  "first_name": "lizi",
  "last_name": "nanana"
}

### 2. Register - Duplicate Email (should return 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "lizizizi@gmail.com",
  "password": "differentpassword",
  "first_name": "lizi",
  "last_name": "nanana"
}